# dissect-extract

This project builds on the [dissect framework](https://docs.dissect.tools) to automatically extract common triage artifacts from one or more targets, super-timeline and label. Includes a configurable set of targeted artifacts for each major operating system family (Windows, Unix, Mac OS).

Currently includes artifacts sets for:

- Lateral Movement
- Data Access
- Data Exfiltration
- Persistence and Execution

Planned:

- Credential Access
- Defense Evasion

## Requirements

Install `dissect` via pip(x|xu) install
